name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Siixx Fox
description: Agent Siixx was originally a bandit leader of an intergalactic gang that stole from wealthy imperials. It wasn't until Agent Siixx met Big Trezz and developed a bond that he decided to give up thieving for a bigger cause. He's still a master pickpocket, safe cracker, weapons expert, and incredible poker player. His favorite weapon is an energy katana blade that can emit poison.
